data.title: Does Baidu’s AI Investment Justify Its 37% Rally in 2025?
data.description: Curious if Baidu is really a good deal or just another pricey tech play? You are not alone. A closer look at the numbers might surprise you. Baidu’s stock has posted a 40.7% year-to-date gain and is up 37.2% over the past year, but dipped 9.6% in the last month. This reflects shifting market sentiment. Recent news has highlighted Baidu's ongoing advances in artificial intelligence, with increased investment in large language models and strategic partnerships capturing headlines. These...
